									</a>
								</li>
																								<li class="cat-post-item">
									<a rel="nofollow" class="cat-post-thumbnail  cat-post-none" href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/government/census-data-national-distribution-federal-funding/" rel="bookmark" title="How the 2020 census will guide the distribution of $1.5 trillion in federal funding">
										<span class="rthumb">
																							<img width="75" height="75" src="https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/pepi-stojanovski-MJSFNZ8BAXw-unsplash-75x75.jpg" class="attachment-sidethumb size-sidethumb wp-post-image" alt="hundred dollar bills" title="" srcset="https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/pepi-stojanovski-MJSFNZ8BAXw-unsplash-75x75.jpg 75w, https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/pepi-stojanovski-MJSFNZ8BAXw-unsplash-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 75px) 100vw, 75px" />																					</span>
